=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex24 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with complex oscillator character around 51 Hz, featuring punchy attack and compressed envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with lowpass character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: compressed
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: lowpass
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 51.4651
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.0248
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0678
  pitch_clarity: 13.3813
  inharmonicity: 0.0423
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -0.0102
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
